   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://fallenalliance.org/screenshots/cecil_20020408123732.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Upgrade advice needed please...</span><hr size=1> Royal Frosted Velium Vambs (or guardian maybe)<br><br>Most obvious upgrade to me though is your mask.  Get one with some AC and some HP on it. <p><a href=http://www.fallenalliance.org/scripts/members/profile.pl?who=Memnenth>Sir Memnenth Peredhil</a><br>Guildleader - <a href=http://www.fallenalliance.org>Fallen Alliance</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utigerheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tigerheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 205<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 6:34:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Upgrade advice needed please...</span><hr size=1> Get rid of your bow , and replace it with an Idol of the Thorned(5k) 10ac 7STR 10STa. If you dont want to spend alot of plat, replace it with a goranga Idol (500 to 1K) 8AC 3dex 2agi 25hp.<br><br>   anyways  anything is better than a Bow tieing up a slot when you can gain AC and stats. We suck at archery anyways. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=152485">Tigerheart</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umadren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Madren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 72<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 7:53:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Upgrade advice needed please...</span><hr size=1> a very easy quest for you would be iced forged shackles. no drop bracer 10ac 5dex str agi 30hp.<br><br>mask / range  are glaring needs. ( someone already mentioned the obvious ones for range )<br><br>masks you can get a sebilite scale mask pretty cheap ( 8ac 4wis 4fire/pois 10hp ( i think) - medium sizes only<br><br>Legs -  Dragonhide from west wastes prices are falling, even the cheap ones are good ( 22ac 4stam 8dex )<br><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=36881">Sir Madren Steelhand</a><br>Cestus Dei<br>Veeshan <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usaleani.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saleani</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Wandering Knight</span><br>  Posts: 130<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 8:02:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Upgrade advice needed please...</span><hr size=1> Guants: crystal chitin might be an upgrade to consider for you: ac20, str 10. Rather common drop in velks, from the camp that drops the haste guantlets, so you should spend a lot less than 1k.<br><br>If you like to quest, you are of the level to do the cougarskin mask in iceclad ocean. ac 6 and a few stats, only takes 2 hq cougarskin pelts and 2 mammoth meats.<br><br>If you have a good relationship with a grandmaster smith (human, with skill near 250), try to get one of the new bracers made. Might cost you all your plat and then some though. <br><br>Radiant Heraldic Bracer (that's the E-marr imbue, other deity imbues give almost the same stats.)<br>AC 25, wis 5, mana 30, hp 30, +5 all saves.<br><br>E-marrinbue is close to deepwater look, Rodcet nife (mine) is pinkish like the ralukan from umbral plains.<br><br>I just got mine made last night and I expect it to be primary gear up to high 50s (or even 60). It has a recommended level of 45, so the ac and other stats may be reduced until then. It eats a blue diamond as part of the recipe, so don't be surprised if the price you get is measured in blue diamonds. <p><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64195'>Combat Profile</a><br><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64207'>Tradeskill Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=ensis>Ensis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 9:46:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Upgrade advice needed please...</span><hr size=1> I do have a goranga idol, I just forgot to put it in my profile.  In terms of leggings, are the deepwater leggins really worth 20K (about what they go at for my server)?  Perhaps I should keep saving for them.  <br><br>I'll look into the CC gaunts, I see them going for pretty cheap on my server..<br><br><br>Thanks for advice all!<br><br>Ensis <p>Ensis<br>Paladin of Erollisi Marr<br>Guild Leader of Fortune and Glory</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uangelsyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Angelsyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 453<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 11:16:22 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Upgrade advice needed please...</span><hr size=1> At the very least, get some Gauntlets of the Black.<br><br>If there's a high skill (220+) Potter around, get a <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://members.aol.com/karenwilder/idol.jpg">Golden Idol of Erollisi Marr</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.  AC 8, +5 Wis, +5 Cha, +40 Mana, +9 DR. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhakashakamalakabalsaka.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Haka Shakamalakabalsaka</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 279<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(5/31/02 11:28:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> Replace your face...<br><br>Str does do much and the 8wis can be replaced.<br><br>Get a Crystal Eyes mask or something else that has ac/hp on it.<br><br>Focus on AC/Hp your level as much as possible. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=877.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=877.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=877.topic&index=7><img src=http://eq1.castersreal